<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div id="booking" class="border-t border-vroom-line py-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vroom-ink">Booking</h2>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">How do I book a car?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">Browse the catalog, open a vehicle page, choose your trip dates, then continue to add it to your cart and check out.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">What do I need to rent?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">A valid driver's license, a payment method, and an active Vroom account. Some vehicles may have additional age or insurance requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="payments" class="border-t border-vroom-line py-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vroom-ink">Payments</h2>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">When am I charged?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">You'll see trip totals before taxes on the vehicle page. Final charges are confirmed at checkout. You won't be charged until you complete checkout.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">Are there hidden fees?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">Daily rates are shown upfront. Taxes and any applicable fees appear before you confirm your order.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="cancellations" class="border-t border-vroom-line py-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vroom-ink">Cancellations</h2>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">Can I cancel a booking?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">Yes. Log in, open your profile, and review your orders. Cancellations made 24+ hours before pickup are typically fully refunded.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">How do refunds work?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">Approved refunds are returned to your original payment method. Processing times vary by bank.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="hosting" class="border-t border-vroom-line py-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vroom-ink">Hosting</h2>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-vroom-ink">Can I list my car?</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-vroom-muted">Yes. Contact our team to get started as a host. We'll help you set pricing, availability, and listing details.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4 rounded-3xl border border-vroom-line bg-neutral-50 p-6 text-center sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-vroom-ink">Still need help?</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-vroom-muted">Our support team is available Mon–Fri, 8 AM – 6 PM CT.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary mt-5">Contact support</a>
  </div>
</section>
